title: ‘The Challenge: All Stars’ Season 3, Episodes 1-2 With Derrick | Death, Taxes, and Bananas
description:
Derrick Kosinski joins Johnny Bananas to talk about the Season 3 premiere of ‘All Stars,' including all the drama that went on behind the scenes of the first two episodes.
Host: Johnny Bananas
Guest: Derrick Kosinski
